@@TJvBrowseFolder
Description:
This component is a dialog for the selection of a directory using the shell browse for folder dialog. The dialog supports special features added with IE4.0 and IE5.0 (Resize, Drag and Drop, Files, Urls, ...) and select the last directory choosed (the directory specified in the Directory property) when opening the dialog for a second time.

